  "description": "Add large biomes world type as separate dimension.",
  "body": "# Large Biomes Dimension\n\nLarge Biomes Dimension add large biomes world type as separate dimension.\n\n![Preview](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/Fo9Xodfg/images/7b123c13dfd8c8cf49d673586be3812af5c8287d.jpeg)\n\n## Usage\n\nTo access Large Biomes Dimension, make portal with obsidian frame and grass block on both top frame corner and stone on both bottom frame corner like this:\n\n![Large Biomes Dimension Portal](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f01744e55af0c4c14112110e004ac21c837af76.png)\n\n## Compatibility\n\n- Geophilic\n- Tectonic\n- TerraBlender (Biomes O' Plenty, Oh The Biomes We've Gone, Regions Unexplored, etc)\n- [Passengers Portal Fix](https://modrinth.com/project/LI0BrUQA)\n- **Create** Addons: [Create: Portal Integration](https://modrinth.com/project/2f4ngcAb)\n\n## Issues\n\nThere are no new compatibility issues or bugs being reported. Please report it on [GitHub](https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-largebiomesdimension/issues) so it can be fixed.\n\n## Support\n\n🟩 26.1-26.1.2 / 🟩 1.21.1 / 🟥 1.21-1.21.11 / 🟩 1.20.1 / 🟪 1.16.5 / 🟪 1.12.2\n\n🟩 Supported  \n🟥 Support Dropped  \n🟨 In Progress  \n🟪 Considered  \n\n## Note\n\nFeel free to use in modpacks, videos, stream, or similar media. Consider help me financially if you like this mod, I will be really grateful.\n\n<br />\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/social/github-plural_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"See me on GitHub\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/mahmudindes\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/available/curseforge_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Available on CurseForge\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@oreno69\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/social/youtube-singular_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Watch me on YouTube\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/cuYgFmq3kz\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/social/discord-singular_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Chat with me on Discord\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://patreon.com/mahmudindes\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/donate/patreon-singular_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Support me on Patreon\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/oreno\"><img src=\"https://github.com/intergrav/devins-badges/blob/v3/assets/compact-minimal/donate/kofi-singular-alt_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Support me on Ko-fi\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://saweria.co/mahmudindes\"><img src=\"https://github.com/barraIhsan/devins-badges/blob/saweria/assets/compact-minimal/donate/saweria-singular_46h.png?raw=true\" alt=\"Support me on Saweria\"></a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dimensionfixer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-dimensionfixer/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/dimensionfixer/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Dimension Fixer\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dimensionlink\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-dimensionlink/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/dimensionlink/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Dimension Link\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/worldportal\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-worldportal/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/worldportal/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"World Portal\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/vanillaworld\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-vanillaworld/blob/master/common/src/main/resources/assets/vanillaworld/icon.png?raw=true\" width=\"96\" height=\"96\" alt=\"Vanilla World\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/morecatvariants\"><img src=\"https://github.com/mahmudindev/mcmod-morecatvariants/blob/master/common/src/main/resource